content: I am new one on FHIR,I am trying to implement the FHir resource by using Java.can any one help on this
I would start with the FHIR downloads page -- http://hl7.org/fhir/downloads.html -- and then follow the link to the HAPI-FHIR project by James Agnew -- http://jamesagnew.github.io/hapi-fhir/
